{"tid":1909442,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"爭咩呀，叫「721 831紀念公園」呀笨","createTime":"2020-03-04T03:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T03:52:16.000Z","uid":323380,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4a46368614053c2e1f85ab25fa67eb122bb5c12b","tid":1909442,"uid":323380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"我都唔明班議員諗乜，搵位俾人入，花式自殺。<strong><ins>先自聲明</ins></strong>，周梓樂陳彥霖係好慘，死得不明不白，但有冇人有真憑實據企出黎指控港共政府謀殺？？老實講，連佢地係咪抗爭者都唔肯定。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">擺佢地上神檯，搞到件事失曬焦，凝聚唔到黃營，又俾到藍絲打親情法律牌，唔洗幾日就收皮。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大佬，有咁多令人髮指的暴行慘劇唔用，邊個天才話要用人名㗎？台灣有個228和平紀念公園，喺香港，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721同831先係整場運動嘅轉捩點，全城connect</span></span>。你同下一代講反送中，一定會講721 831，呢啲先係穩打穩紮嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公民教育</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n仲嘈咩呀，叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「721 831紀念公園」</strong></span></span>啦！<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，班新任區議員麻煩醒醒目目，唔係可以guan多幾多舖㗎咋。"},{"pid":"de9f4c30b20638ebf367292d2d8f0f651b794cdb","tid":1909442,"uid":157261,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:21:40.000Z","msg":"彥霖可能真係未知<br />\n周梓樂你話唔知係木咪抗爭者..<br />\n你走先la"},{"pid":"5d22c17209c18a60b6bd3e31efb5095830e2b135","tid":1909442,"uid":113074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:21:42.000Z","msg":"改咁多名，唔知嘅仲以為光復咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d7949020b7a1a57f516bb866d6e1dd1339662a","tid":1909442,"uid":167506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:26:23.000Z","msg":"我都唔明點解一定要用人名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb501c5a62ea29fee8dec8a3459090d72903ce0","tid":1909442,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:27:53.000Z","msg":"好主意"},{"pid":"d5aa1a0f9870ed61014b494b52a